snippet.title: Showbiz Junkies
snippet.description:
Everything to do with entertainment including interviews with actors, directors, writer, singers, and other celebrities, along with a selection of trailers and clips from movies and TV shows.

Showbiz Junkie's Editor-in-Chief Rebecca Murray spent far too much time standing around on red carpets patiently (for the most part) waiting to interview celebrities.  Hundreds of those older interviews spanning nearly two decades are currently in the process of being moved onto this YouTube channel. So if you notice older interviews newly uploaded, it's not because we're traveling back in time - it's because we're consolidating all interviews to YouTube.
